# Debug Workflow

## Crawler issues
- SSL error → check `verify=False` in requests call
- 403/blocked → check User-Agent header ("Mozilla/5.0 Windows...")
- PDF not downloaded → check SHA256 already exists in DB (idempotent)
- DB error → check DATABASE_URL and postgres service health

## Indexer issues
- Qdrant connection → check QDRANT_URL, `curl $QDRANT_URL/healthz`
- Embedding error → check OPENROUTER_API_KEY, model name `openai/text-embedding-3-large`
- Empty chunks → check PDF parsing with `python3 -c "import pymupdf4llm; print(pymupdf4llm.to_markdown('file.pdf')[:500])"`

## Bot issues
- OpenClaw 401 → check OPENCLAW_API_KEY matches sidecar config
- Empty search results → check Qdrant collection exists and has data
- JSON parse error from LLM → check system prompt forces JSON output

## Full debug flow
1. `./scripts/health.sh` — check all services running
2. `./scripts/logs.sh [service] 100` — check recent logs
3. Check specific component interactively
